": "Q_622731566", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "医学生力量训练会影响以后的外科手术吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "（以下更新了第二问。望指教）本人大二医学生，以后希望进入外科。接触健身一年多，进步自己感觉不算慢，现在卧推 90kg 可以做组，但一直有顾虑，盲目的上大重量力量训练，很多都需要用手，想问问医学前辈和健身大佬，这些力量训练（卧推、硬拉、引体等等需要用手的），是否会影响以后的外科手术操作精度？ 看了各路大佬、前辈的回答和建议，受益匪浅，其实关于外科科室的选择我也很迷茫现在，我觉得兴趣在我这影响可能不大，我更多希望去发展潜力更大的科室，（很多前辈说可以去骨科，虽然是随口一提但我还是想问问），各位前辈、大佬愿意指点一下未来方向吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/622731566"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iqez3u/ynrZM8EAMaCTEwMDY2NDExMiDQtqSoBjAAOHBAMHIJNjIyNzMxNTY2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1695515292.100289", "card_id": "Q_623262503", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 283}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "可以看看你手机里的天空吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-d58f8fad2b790ff00fe12b6e7080ac92_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/623262503"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIqez3u/ynrZM8EAMaCTEwMDc4MjIyMyCJjbSoBjAAOMMCQDFyCTYyMzI2MjUwM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1688912188092293120", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/topic/20234771/hot", "title": "杭州亚运会", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTY4ODkxMjE4ODA5MjI5MzEyMHITMTY4ODkxMjE4ODA5MjI5MzEyMHgA", "tag": "话题", "tag_bg_color": "GRD07A"}, {"id": "1683447529524715520", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu